{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":500,"text":"I'm a bug lover, myself --"},{"time":2523,"text":"not from childhood, by the way,"},{"time":4300,"text":"but rather late."},{"time":6897,"text":"When I bachelored,"},{"time":8300,"text":"majoring in zoology\nat Tel Aviv University,"},{"time":11017,"text":"I kind of fell in love with bugs."},{"time":13178,"text":"And then, within zoology,"},{"time":14940,"text":"I took the course\nor the discipline of entomology,"},{"time":18104,"text":"the science of insects."},{"time":20744,"text":"And then I thought to myself,\nhow can I be practical"},{"time":23966,"text":"or help in the science of entomology?"},{"time":27300,"text":"And then I moved to the world\nof plant protection --"},{"time":30557,"text":"plant protection from insects,"},{"time":33083,"text":"from bad bugs."},{"time":34921,"text":"And then within plant protection,"},{"time":37300,"text":"I came into the discipline\nof biological pest control,"},{"time":41585,"text":"which we actually define"},{"time":43299,"text":"as the use of living organisms"},{"time":46300,"text":"to reduce populations\nof noxious plant pests."},{"time":50824,"text":"So it's a whole discipline\nin plant protection"},{"time":53950,"text":"aimed at the reduction of chemicals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58196,"text":"And biological pest control, by the way,"},{"time":60266,"text":"or these \"good bugs\"\nthat we are talking about,"},{"time":63058,"text":"they've existed in the world\nfor thousands and thousands of years,"},{"time":66914,"text":"for a long, long time."},{"time":68541,"text":"But only in the last 120 years,"},{"time":72228,"text":"people started, or people\nknew more and more"},{"time":75642,"text":"how to exploit, or how to use,\nthis biological control phenomenon,"},{"time":80052,"text":"or in fact, natural control phenomenon,"},{"time":83456,"text":"for their own needs."},{"time":86180,"text":"Because biological control phenomenon --\nyou can see it in your backyard."},{"time":89812,"text":"Just take a magnifying glass.\nYou see what I have here?"},{"time":92792,"text":"That's a magnifier, times 10."},{"time":96830,"text":"You just open it, twist leaves,"},{"time":99852,"text":"and you see a whole new world\nof minute insects,"},{"time":103300,"text":"or little spiders of one millimeter,\none-and-a-half, two millimeters long,"},{"time":108300,"text":"and you can distinguish\nbetween the good ones and the bad ones."},{"time":111324,"text":"So this phenomenon of natural control\nexists literally everywhere."},{"time":115888,"text":"Here, in front of this building, I'm sure."},{"time":117966,"text":"Just have a look at the plants."},{"time":119905,"text":"So it's everywhere,\nand we need to know how to exploit it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124069,"text":"Well, let's go hand by hand"},{"time":126070,"text":"and browse through just a few examples."},{"time":129300,"text":"What is a pest?"},{"time":130839,"text":"What damage does it actually\ninflict on the plant?"},{"time":134173,"text":"And what is the natural enemy,"},{"time":136458,"text":"the biological control agent,\nor the \"good bug\""},{"time":139465,"text":"that we're talking about?"},{"time":140690,"text":"In general, I'm going to talk\nabout insects and spiders,"},{"time":145727,"text":"or mites, let us call them."},{"time":147974,"text":"Insects, those six-legged organisms"},{"time":150767,"text":"and spiders or mites,\nthe eight-legged organisms."},{"time":154869,"text":"Let's have a look at that."},{"time":156300,"text":"Here is a devastating pest, a spider mite,"},{"time":159552,"text":"because it does a lot\nof webbing, like a spider."},{"time":162800,"text":"You see the mother in between,"},{"time":164346,"text":"and two daughters, probably,\non the left and right,"},{"time":166780,"text":"and a single egg on the right-hand side."},{"time":168872,"text":"And then you see\nwhat kind of damage it can inflict."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171384,"text":"On your right-hand side,\nyou can see a cucumber leaf,"},{"time":173950,"text":"in the middle, a cotton leaf,"},{"time":175415,"text":"and on the left, a tomato leaf\nwith these little stipplings."},{"time":178637,"text":"They can literally turn\nfrom green to white,"},{"time":181714,"text":"because of the sucking, piercing\nmouth parts of those spiders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187758,"text":"But here comes nature,\nthat provides us with a good spider."},{"time":191452,"text":"This is a predatory mite --\njust as small as a spider mite;"},{"time":194858,"text":"one, two millimeters long,\nnot more than that --"},{"time":197686,"text":"running quickly, hunting,\nchasing the spider mites."},{"time":202124,"text":"And here, you can see this lady\nin action on your left-hand side --"},{"time":206016,"text":"just pierces, sucks the body fluids\non the left-hand side of the pest mite."},{"time":211666,"text":"And after five minutes,\nthis is what you see:"},{"time":214300,"text":"just a typical dead corpse --"},{"time":216643,"text":"the shriveled, sucked-out,\ndead corpse of the spider mite,"},{"time":220300,"text":"and next to it, two satiated\nindividuals, predatory mites,"},{"time":225188,"text":"a mother on the left-hand side,\na young nymph on the right-hand side."},{"time":228709,"text":"By the way, a meal for them for 24 hours,"},{"time":231655,"text":"is about five of the spider mites,\nof the bad mites,"},{"time":235929,"text":"and-or 15 to 20 eggs of the pest mites."},{"time":240838,"text":"By the way, they are always hungry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243300,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":245563,"text":"And here is another example: aphids."},{"time":247894,"text":"It's springtime now in Israel."},{"time":249772,"text":"When temperatures rise sharply,"},{"time":252301,"text":"you can see those bad ones,\nthose aphids, all over the plants --"},{"time":255598,"text":"in your hibiscus, in your lantana,"},{"time":258300,"text":"in the young, fresh foliage\nof the so-called spring flush."},{"time":262300,"text":"By the way, with aphids you have\nonly females, like Amazons."},{"time":266300,"text":"Females giving rise to females,\ngiving rise to other females."},{"time":269749,"text":"No males at all."},{"time":271002,"text":"Parthenogenesis, as it's so called."},{"time":273462,"text":"And they're very happy\nwith that, apparently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275601,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":276650,"text":"Here we can see the damage."},{"time":278300,"text":"Those aphids secrete a sticky,\nsugary liquid called honeydew,"},{"time":285084,"text":"and this just clogs\nthe upper parts of the plant."},{"time":289127,"text":"Here you see a typical cucumber leaf\nthat turned from green to black"},{"time":292864,"text":"because of a black fungus, sooty mold,\nwhich is covering it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297607,"text":"And here comes the salvation,\nthrough this parasitic wasp."},{"time":302959,"text":"Here we are not talking about a predator."},{"time":305085,"text":"Here we are talking a parasite --"},{"time":307573,"text":"not a two-legged parasite,"},{"time":309470,"text":"but an eight-legged parasite, of course."},{"time":312503,"text":"This is a parasitic wasp,"},{"time":314301,"text":"again, two millimeters long, slender,\na very quick and sharp flier."},{"time":320080,"text":"And here you can see\nthis parasite in action,"},{"time":322888,"text":"like in an acrobatic maneuver."},{"time":325579,"text":"She stands vis-Ã -vis"},{"time":327300,"text":"in front of the victim\nat the right-hand side,"},{"time":329651,"text":"bending its abdomen\nand inserting a single egg"},{"time":334849,"text":"into the body fluids of the aphid."},{"time":337638,"text":"By the way, the aphid tries to escape."},{"time":339819,"text":"She kicks and bites\nand secretes different liquids,"},{"time":344102,"text":"but nothing will happen, in fact --"},{"time":346176,"text":"only the egg of the parasitoid\nwill be inserted"},{"time":349610,"text":"into the body fluids of the aphid."},{"time":351772,"text":"And after a few days,\ndepending upon temperature,"},{"time":354732,"text":"the egg will hatch"},{"time":356173,"text":"and the larva of this parasite\nwill eat the aphid from the inside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361168,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":362243,"text":"This is all natural. This is all natural."},{"time":364511,"text":"This is not fiction, nothing at all."},{"time":366534,"text":"Again -- in your backyard.\nIn your backyard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369509,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":371038,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":372527,"text":"But this is the end result: mummies."},{"time":379094,"text":"This is the visual result\nof a dead aphid encompassing inside,"},{"time":384300,"text":"a developing parasitoid that,\nafter a few minutes, you see halfway out."},{"time":390219,"text":"The birth is almost complete."},{"time":392449,"text":"You can see, by the way,\nin different movies, etc.,"},{"time":395647,"text":"it takes just a few minutes."},{"time":397300,"text":"And if this is a female,\nshe'll immediately mate with a male"},{"time":400826,"text":"and off she goes,\nbecause time is very short."},{"time":403686,"text":"This female can live\nonly three to four days,"},{"time":406300,"text":"and she needs to give rise\nto around 400 eggs."},{"time":410186,"text":"That means she has 400 bad aphids"},{"time":413612,"text":"to put her eggs into their body fluids."},{"time":417204,"text":"This is, of course, not the end of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419204,"text":"There is a whole wealth\nof other natural enemies"},{"time":421610,"text":"and this is just the last example."},{"time":423300,"text":"Again, we'll start first with the pest:"},{"time":425817,"text":"the thrips."},{"time":427300,"text":"By the way, all these weird names --"},{"time":429627,"text":"I didn't bother you with the Latin\nnames of these creatures,"},{"time":433150,"text":"just the popular names."},{"time":434414,"text":"But this is a nice,\nslender, very bad pest."},{"time":438550,"text":"If you can see this: sweet peppers."},{"time":440922,"text":"This is not just an exotic,\nornamental sweet pepper."},{"time":443945,"text":"This is a sweet pepper\nwhich is not consumable"},{"time":446516,"text":"because it is suffering\nfrom a viral disease"},{"time":449300,"text":"transmitted by those thrip adults."},{"time":452910,"text":"And here comes the natural enemy,\nminute pirate bug --"},{"time":456451,"text":"\"minute,\" because it is rather small."},{"time":459054,"text":"Here you can see the adult,\nblack, and two young ones."},{"time":462497,"text":"And again, in action."},{"time":464066,"text":"This adult pierces the thrips,"},{"time":467614,"text":"sucking it within just several minutes,"},{"time":469884,"text":"going to the other prey,\ncontinuing all over the place."},{"time":473138,"text":"And if we spread those minute\npirate bugs, the good ones,"},{"time":477457,"text":"for example, in a sweet pepper plot,"},{"time":480377,"text":"they go to the flowers."},{"time":481970,"text":"And look -- this flower is flooded\nwith predatory bugs, with the good ones,"},{"time":487078,"text":"after wiping out the bad ones, the thrips."},{"time":490300,"text":"So this is a very positive situation."},{"time":492908,"text":"No harm to the developing fruit.\nNo harm to the fruit set."},{"time":496232,"text":"Everything is just fine\nunder these circumstances."},{"time":500045,"text":"But again, the question is,"},{"time":501530,"text":"here you saw them on a one-to-one basis --\nthe pest, the natural enemy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506097,"text":"What we do is actually this."},{"time":509544,"text":"In Northeast Israel,\nin Kibbutz Sde Eliyahu,"},{"time":512997,"text":"there is a facility that mass-produces\nthose natural enemies."},{"time":517711,"text":"In other words, what we do there\nis amplify the natural control,"},{"time":524213,"text":"or the biological control phenomenon."},{"time":526214,"text":"And in 30,000 square meters\nof state-of-the-art greenhouses,"},{"time":531115,"text":"there, we are mass-producing\nthose predatory mites,"},{"time":534443,"text":"those minute pirate bugs,"},{"time":536162,"text":"those parasitic wasps, etc."},{"time":539082,"text":"Many different parts."},{"time":540433,"text":"By the way, they have\na very nice landscape --"},{"time":542713,"text":"you see the Jordanian Mountains\non the one hand,"},{"time":545113,"text":"and the Jordan Valley on the other hand,"},{"time":547114,"text":"and a good, mild winter\nand a nice, hot summer,"},{"time":551191,"text":"which is an excellent condition\nto mass-produce those creatures."},{"time":555210,"text":"And by the way, mass-production --\nit is not genetic manipulation."},{"time":559474,"text":"There are no GMOs -- genetically\nmodified organisms -- whatsoever."},{"time":563545,"text":"We take them from nature,"},{"time":565300,"text":"and the only thing that we do\nis give them the optimal conditions,"},{"time":569621,"text":"under the greenhouses\nor in the climate rooms,"},{"time":572300,"text":"in order to proliferate,\nmultiply and reproduce."},{"time":576367,"text":"And that's what we get."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578082,"text":"You see under a microscope."},{"time":579963,"text":"You see in the upper left corner?\nYou see a single predatory mite."},{"time":583131,"text":"And this is the whole bunch\nof predatory mites."},{"time":586550,"text":"You see this ampul. You see this one."},{"time":588894,"text":"I have one gram of those predatory mites."},{"time":592391,"text":"One gram is 80,000 individuals."},{"time":596503,"text":"80,000 individuals are good enough\nto control one acre,"},{"time":602113,"text":"4,000 square meters,"},{"time":603975,"text":"of a strawberry plot"},{"time":605852,"text":"against spider mites for the whole season"},{"time":608805,"text":"of almost one year."},{"time":610982,"text":"And we can produce\nfrom this, believe you me,"},{"time":614554,"text":"several dozens of kilograms\non an annual basis."},{"time":618980,"text":"So this is what I call\namplification of the phenomenon."},{"time":623212,"text":"And no, we do not disrupt the balance."},{"time":627035,"text":"On the contrary,"},{"time":628300,"text":"because we bring it to every cultural plot"},{"time":631207,"text":"where the balance was already disrupted"},{"time":633984,"text":"by the chemicals."},{"time":635300,"text":"Here we come with those natural enemies"},{"time":637201,"text":"in order to reverse\na little bit of the wheel"},{"time":640132,"text":"and to bring more natural balance\nto the agricultural plot"},{"time":644138,"text":"by reducing those chemicals."},{"time":646003,"text":"That's the whole idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647582,"text":"And what is the impact?"},{"time":649044,"text":"In this table, you can\nactually see what is an impact"},{"time":652300,"text":"of a successful biological\ncontrol by good bugs."},{"time":656648,"text":"For example, in Israel, where we employ\nmore than 1,000 hectares --"},{"time":663041,"text":"10,000 dunams in Israeli terms --"},{"time":665740,"text":"of biological pests\ncontrolling sweet pepper"},{"time":668389,"text":"under protection,"},{"time":669937,"text":"75 percent of the pesticides\nwere actually reduced."},{"time":673616,"text":"And Israeli strawberries, even more --"},{"time":676125,"text":"80 percent of the pesticides,"},{"time":677923,"text":"especially those aimed\nagainst pest mites in strawberries."},{"time":682846,"text":"So the impact is very strong."},{"time":685984,"text":"And there goes the question,"},{"time":688156,"text":"especially if you ask\ngrowers, agriculturists:"},{"time":691157,"text":"Why biological control?"},{"time":692874,"text":"Why good bugs?"},{"time":694676,"text":"By the way, the number of answers you get"},{"time":697466,"text":"equals the number of people you ask."},{"time":701054,"text":"But if we go, for example,\nto this place, Southeast Israel,"},{"time":705636,"text":"the Arava area\nabove the Great Rift Valley,"},{"time":709136,"text":"where the pearl of Israeli\nagriculture is located,"},{"time":714205,"text":"especially under greenhouse conditions,\nor under screenhouse conditions --"},{"time":717822,"text":"if you drive all the way\nto Eilat, you see this"},{"time":720635,"text":"just in the middle of the desert."},{"time":722572,"text":"And if you zoom in,"},{"time":724105,"text":"you can definitely watch this:"},{"time":726196,"text":"grandparents with their grandchildren,"},{"time":728407,"text":"distributing the natural\nenemies, the good bugs,"},{"time":731300,"text":"instead of wearing special clothes"},{"time":733697,"text":"and gas masks and applying chemicals."},{"time":736485,"text":"So safety, with respect\nto the application,"},{"time":739095,"text":"is the number one answer\nthat we get from growers,"},{"time":742538,"text":"for \"Why biological control?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":745689,"text":"Number two, many growers\nare, in fact, petrified"},{"time":749683,"text":"by the idea of resistance,"},{"time":752890,"text":"that the pests will become\nresistant to the chemicals,"},{"time":757467,"text":"just like in our case, that bacteria\nbecomes resistant to antibiotics."},{"time":761300,"text":"It's the same, and it can\nhappen very quickly."},{"time":764908,"text":"Fortunately, in either biological control\nor even natural control,"},{"time":769300,"text":"resistance is extremely rare."},{"time":772940,"text":"It hardly happens."},{"time":774513,"text":"Because this is evolution,\nthis is the natural ratio,"},{"time":777889,"text":"unlike resistance, which happens\nin the case of chemicals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":781767,"text":"And thirdly, public demand."},{"time":785236,"text":"The more the public demands\nthe reduction of chemicals,"},{"time":790064,"text":"the more growers become aware of the fact"},{"time":793933,"text":"that they should, wherever they can\nand wherever possible,"},{"time":796699,"text":"replace the chemical control\nwith biological control."},{"time":800734,"text":"Even here, there is another grower,"},{"time":802820,"text":"you see, very interested in the bugs,\nthe bad ones and the good ones,"},{"time":806571,"text":"wearing this magnifier\nalready on her head,"},{"time":808790,"text":"just walking safely in her crop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":811867,"text":"Finally, I want to get to my vision,"},{"time":815151,"text":"or, in fact, to my dream."},{"time":817611,"text":"Because, you see, this is the reality."},{"time":819658,"text":"Have a look at the gap."},{"time":821158,"text":"If we take the overall turnover"},{"time":823300,"text":"of the biocontrol industry worldwide,"},{"time":825769,"text":"it's 250 million dollars."},{"time":828762,"text":"And look at the overall pesticide industry"},{"time":831880,"text":"in all the crops throughout the world."},{"time":834077,"text":"I think it's times 100\nor something like that."},{"time":836972,"text":"Twenty-five billion."},{"time":838702,"text":"So there is a huge gap to bridge."},{"time":842300,"text":"So actually, how can we do it?"},{"time":843988,"text":"How can we bridge, or let's say,\nnarrow, this gap over the years?"},{"time":848892,"text":"First of all, we need to find more robust,"},{"time":852664,"text":"good and reliable biological solutions,"},{"time":855300,"text":"more good bugs that we can\neither mass-produce"},{"time":859947,"text":"or actually conserve in the field."},{"time":863013,"text":"Secondly, to create even more intensive\nand strict public demand"},{"time":867623,"text":"for the reduction of chemicals\nin agricultural fresh produce."},{"time":871716,"text":"And thirdly, also to increase\nawareness by the growers"},{"time":875498,"text":"to the potential of this industry."},{"time":878300,"text":"And this gap really narrows."},{"time":880823,"text":"Step by step, it does narrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":884557,"text":"So I think my last slide is:"},{"time":886786,"text":"All we are saying --\nwe can actually sing it --"},{"time":889075,"text":"Give nature a chance."},{"time":890893,"text":"I'm saying it on behalf\nof all the biocontrol practitioners"},{"time":894083,"text":"and implementers,"},{"time":895421,"text":"in Israel and abroad,"},{"time":897666,"text":"really give nature a chance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":899722,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900905,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}